YPScraper - Scrapy-based scraper for YellowPages.com

Example:
$ scrapy runspider yellowpages/yellowpages/spiders/yellow.py -a search_terms="Casino" -a geo_location_terms="Las Vegas, NV" -o casinos.csv

This will scrape business from:
https://www.yellowpages.com/search?search_terms=Casinos&geo_location_terms=Las+Vegas%2C+NV


